{
  "texts": [
    "It also contributes to the writing process by paraphrasing the user's text in different styles, and checks texts for AI presence.",
    "Products such as genei (https://www.genei.io/), Notion (https://www.notion.so/product), and Iris.ai (https://iris.ai/) present themselves as workspaces that help users organize their research data in addition to having GAI features.",
    "Genei, for example, offers a search engine and the ability to extract keywords or summaries from search results or user uploaded documents that can be stored with other files on the platform.",
    "It additionally includes a citation generator and a tool that rephrases or expands users' writing.",
    "As we will discuss further below, these multi-function platforms may have an edge in the market because of their ability to combine the capabilities of multiple tools being marketed separately into one workspace."
  ]
}